Package: smartLR
Type: Package
Title: Smart Computational Linear Regression
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Wing Lo
Maintainer: Wing Lo <wclo@ucdavis.edu>
Description: Smart Computational Linear Regression.
    Automatically select Armadillo Linear algebra method or
    R base lm method based on the dimension of data.
    Also support estimation of bootstrap with the 
    support of parallel computing.
